				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\sqrt{s}=14$$\end{document} TeV pp collisions at the IP5, IP8 and IP1, respectively (see also Sect. 1.6).Table 3
