				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$p_\text {T} > 30$$\end{document} GeV), and they are sensitive only to lepton-number-violating (LNV) neutrino decays.

